    "parse": {
      "title": "Mutant Bug Lair",
      "pageid": 5809,
      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"floatright\"><a href=\"/File:Mutant_Bug_Lair.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Mutant Bug Lair.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Mutant_Bug_Lair.png/320px-Mutant_Bug_Lair.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"320\" height=\"239\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Mutant_Bug_Lair.png/480px-Mutant_Bug_Lair.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/47/Mutant_Bug_Lair.png 2x\" /></a></div>\n<p>The <b>Mutant Bug Lair</b> is an underground location that becomes accessible as part of the <a href=\"/Quests#Dark_Talisman\" title=\"Quests\">Dark Talisman Quest</a>. The entrance to the lair is in the northwest corner of <a href=\"/The_Sewers\" title=\"The Sewers\">The Sewers</a>. Talking to <a href=\"/Krobus\" title=\"Krobus\">Krobus</a> during this quest will open the passage to this location.\n</p><p>The player should be prepared to encounter <a href=\"/Monsters\" title=\"Monsters\">monsters</a> before entering the Mutant Bug Lair because there are a number of <a href=\"/Mutant_Grub\" title=\"Mutant Grub\">Mutant Grubs</a> and <a href=\"/Mutant_Fly\" title=\"Mutant Fly\">Mutant Flies</a> inside.\n</p><p>Even though plants are growing here and <a href=\"/Fishing\" title=\"Fishing\">fishing</a> is possible, the game considers this location to be underground.  Therefore, <a href=\"/Foraging\" title=\"Foraging\">forageable</a> items and <a href=\"/Artifact_Spot\" title=\"Artifact Spot\">artifact spots</a> never spawn here.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Quests\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quests</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Fishing\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Fishing</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Gallery\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Gallery</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quests\">Quests</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Mutant_Bug_Lair&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Quests\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:80%; min-width:500px;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th style=\"width:8%\">Quest Name\n</th>\n<th style=\"width:23%\">Quest Text\n</th>\n<th style=\"width:14%\">Provided By\n</th>\n<th style=\"width:23%\">Requirements\n</th>\n<th style=\"width:12%\">Rewards\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/Quests#Dark_Talisman\" title=\"Quests\">Dark Talisman</a>\n</td>\n<td><i>The Wizard asked me to retrieve the magic ink from his ex-wife's house... but to gain access I'll need a dark talisman. Enter the sewer and ask <a href=\"/Krobus\" title=\"Krobus\">Krobus</a> about the dark talisman.</i>\n</td>\n<td>Enter the <a href=\"/Railroad\" title=\"Railroad\">Railroad</a> area after completing the <a href=\"/Community_Center\" title=\"Community Center\">Community Center</a> <a href=\"/Bundles\" title=\"Bundles\">Bundles</a> or the <a href=\"/Joja_Community_Development_Form\" title=\"Joja Community Development Form\">Joja Community Development Form</a>.\n</td>\n<td>Speak to <a href=\"/Krobus\" title=\"Krobus\">Krobus</a> to gain entrance to the Mutant Bug Lair, then retrieve the Dark Talisman. Return to the <a href=\"/Railroad\" title=\"Railroad\">Railroad</a> area and place the Dark Talisman on the artifact blocking the cave.\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul><li>Unlocks the quest <a href=\"/Quests#Goblin_Problem\" title=\"Quests\">Goblin Problem</a></li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Fishing\">Fishing</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Mutant_Bug_Lair&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Fishing\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:MutantBugLairDistances.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d2/MutantBugLairDistances.png/300px-MutantBugLairDistances.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d2/MutantBugLairDistances.png/450px-MutantBugLairDistances.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d2/MutantBugLairDistances.png/600px-MutantBugLairDistances.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:MutantBugLairDistances.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/Fishing#Distance_from_Land\" title=\"Fishing\">Distances from land</a> in the Mutant Bug Lair</div></div></div>\n<p>The <a href=\"/Slimejack\" title=\"Slimejack\">Slimejack</a> is a unique <a href=\"/Fish\" title=\"Fish\">fish</a> that can only be caught in the Mutant Bug Lair. <a href=\"/Carp\" title=\"Carp\">Carp</a>, <a href=\"/Green_Algae\" title=\"Green Algae\">Green Algae</a>, and <a href=\"/White_Algae\" title=\"White Algae\">White Algae</a> are also possible. The available fish are the same year-round. Fishing here is dangerous because <a href=\"/Mutant_Fly\" title=\"Mutant Fly\">Mutant Flies</a> continuously spawn and attack the player. To avoid this, fish right at the entrance before any bugs are triggered.\n</p><p><br />\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"20\">Time\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:200px; height: 60px; background: #rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.58); text-align: center; font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"display:inline; margin-right:0;\"><img alt=\"All Seasons Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/55/All_Seasons_Icon.png/24px-All_Seasons_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/5/55/All_Seasons_Icon.png 1.5x\" />&#160;<a href=\"/Seasons\" title=\"Seasons\">All</a></span>\n</td>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #9AD4E2;\">6\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #9AD4E2;\">7\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #9AD4E2;\">8\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #9AD4E2;\">9\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #BFF2FF;\">10\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #BFF2FF;\">11\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #BFF2FF;\">12\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #BFF2FF;\">1\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #BFF2FF;\">2\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #A1EDFF;\">3\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #A1EDFF;\">4\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #84C1FF;\">5\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #84C1FF;\">6\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #84C1FF;\">7\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #959FD9;\">8\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #959FD9;\">9\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #959FD9;\">10\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #656A89;\">11\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #656A89;\">12\n</th>\n<th width=\"16\" style=\"background: #656A89;\">1\n</th></tr>\n\n\n\n\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #; text-align: center; line-height:16px;\"><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Carp.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a8/Carp.png/16px-Carp.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a8/Carp.png/24px-Carp.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a8/Carp.png/32px-Carp.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Carp\" title=\"Carp\">Carp</a></span>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"20\" style=\"background: #90CF53; text-align: center; line-height: 16px;\">\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"0\" style=\"display:none; background: #; text-align: center; line-height:16px;\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #; text-align: center; line-height:16px;\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Slimejack.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/34/Slimejack.png/16px-Slimejack.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/34/Slimejack.png/24px-Slimejack.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/3/34/Slimejack.png/32px-Slimejack.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Slimejack\" title=\"Slimejack\">Slimejack</a></span>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"20\" style=\"background: #90CF53; text-align: center; line-height: 16px;\">\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"0\" style=\"display:none; background: #; text-align: center; line-height:16px;\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #; text-align: center; line-height:16px;\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Green Algae.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/6d/Green_Algae.png/16px-Green_Algae.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/6d/Green_Algae.png/24px-Green_Algae.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/6/6d/Green_Algae.png/32px-Green_Algae.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Green_Algae\" title=\"Green Algae\">Green Algae</a></span>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"20\" style=\"background: #90CF53; text-align: center; line-height: 16px;\">\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"0\" style=\"display:none; background: #; text-align: center; line-height:16px;\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #; text-align: center; line-height:16px;\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"White Algae.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f7/White_Algae.png/16px-White_Algae.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f7/White_Algae.png/24px-White_Algae.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f7/White_Algae.png/32px-White_Algae.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/White_Algae\" title=\"White Algae\">White Algae</a></span>\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"20\" style=\"background: #90CF53; text-align: center; line-height: 16px;\">\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"0\" style=\"display:none; background: #; text-align: center; line-height:16px;\">\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\">Gallery</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Mutant_Bug_Lair&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Gallery\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-packed\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 197.33333333333px\"><div style=\"width: 197.33333333333px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 195.33333333333px;\"><div style=\"margin:0px auto;\"><a href=\"/File:Mutant_Bug_Lair_Passage.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/36/Mutant_Bug_Lair_Passage.png/293px-Mutant_Bug_Lair_Passage.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"196\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/36/Mutant_Bug_Lair_Passage.png/439px-Mutant_Bug_Lair_Passage.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/3/36/Mutant_Bug_Lair_Passage.png/585px-Mutant_Bug_Lair_Passage.png 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p>The passage inside <a href=\"/The_Sewers\" title=\"The Sewers\">The Sewers</a> which <a href=\"/Krobus\" title=\"Krobus\">Krobus</a> opens.\n</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 121.33333333333px\"><div style=\"width: 121.33333333333px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 119.33333333333px;\"><div style=\"margin:0px auto;\"><a href=\"/File:Talisman_Chest.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c9/Talisman_Chest.png/179px-Talisman_Chest.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/c/c9/Talisman_Chest.png 1.5x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p>The talisman chest.\n</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Mutant_Bug_Lair&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.1\" title=\"Version History\">1.1</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.11\" title=\"Version History\">1.11</a>: <a href=\"/Weeds\" title=\"Weeds\">Weeds</a> in the Mutant Bug Lair no longer change with the season or turn into <a href=\"/Battery_Pack\" title=\"Battery Pack\">Battery Packs</a> during <a href=\"/Winter\" title=\"Winter\">Winter</a>. Fixed bug where monsters in the Mutant Bug Lair could become the standard grub/fly after saving/reloading the game.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Problematic water tiles fixed, making <a href=\"/Fishing#Distance_from_Land\" title=\"Fishing\">distance-from-land calculations</a> more consistent.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Locations\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Locations\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Backwoods\" title=\"Backwoods\">Backwoods</a> • <a href=\"/The_Beach\" title=\"The Beach\">Beach</a> • <a href=\"/Bus_Stop\" title=\"Bus Stop\">Bus Stop</a> • <a href=\"/The_Desert\" title=\"The Desert\">Calico Desert</a> • <a href=\"/Cindersap_Forest\" title=\"Cindersap Forest\">Cindersap Forest</a> • <a href=\"/The_Farm\" title=\"The Farm\">Farm</a> • <a href=\"/The_Cave\" title=\"The Cave\">Farm Cave</a> • <a href=\"/Farm_Pond\" title=\"Farm Pond\">Farm Pond</a> •  <a href=\"/Graveyard\" title=\"Graveyard\">Graveyard</a> • <a href=\"/Ginger_Island\" title=\"Ginger Island\">Ginger Island</a> • <a href=\"/Mastery_Cave\" title=\"Mastery Cave\">Mastery Cave</a> • <a href=\"/Minecart\" title=\"Minecart\">Minecart</a> • <a href=\"/The_Mines\" title=\"The Mines\">Mines</a> • <a href=\"/The_Mountain\" title=\"The Mountain\">Mountain</a> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mutant Bug Lair</a> • <a href=\"/Pelican_Town\" title=\"Pelican Town\">Pelican Town</a> • <a href=\"/Quarry\" title=\"Quarry\">Quarry</a> • <a href=\"/Quarry_Mine\" title=\"Quarry Mine\">Quarry Mine</a> • <a href=\"/Railroad\" title=\"Railroad\">Railroad</a> • <a href=\"/Secret_Woods\" title=\"Secret Woods\">Secret Woods</a> • <a href=\"/The_Sewers\" title=\"The Sewers\">Sewers</a> • <a href=\"/Skull_Cavern\" title=\"Skull Cavern\">Skull Cavern</a> • <a href=\"/The_Summit\" title=\"The Summit\">Summit</a> • <a href=\"/The_Tunnel\" title=\"The Tunnel\">Tunnel</a> • <a href=\"/Volcano_Dungeon\" title=\"Volcano Dungeon\">Volcano Dungeon</a> • <a href=\"/Witch%27s_Swamp\" title=\"Witch&#39;s Swamp\">Witch's Swamp</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260413231746\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.043 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.051 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1211/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 8245/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 692/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2793/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   30.539      1 -total\n 69.11%   21.105      1 Template:FishLocations_Mutant_Bug_Lair\n 49.15%   15.010      4 Template:FishLocationEntry\n 37.06%   11.319      4 Template:Name\n 12.44%    3.800      1 Template:FishLocationHeader\n 10.44%    3.188      3 Template:History\n  5.96%    1.819      3 Template:Version\n  5.78%    1.764      1 Template:NavboxLocations\n  4.80%    1.465      1 Template:Season\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:5809-0!canonical and timestamp 20260413231746 and revision id 188479\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "[[File:Mutant Bug Lair.png|right|320px]]\nThe '''Mutant Bug Lair''' is an underground location that becomes accessible as part of the [[Quests#Dark Talisman|Dark Talisman Quest]]. The entrance to the lair is in the northwest corner of [[The Sewers]]. Talking to [[Krobus]] during this quest will open the passage to this location.\n\nThe player should be prepared to encounter [[monsters]] before entering the Mutant Bug Lair because there are a number of [[Mutant Grub]]s and [[Mutant Fly|Mutant Flies]] inside.\n\nEven though plants are growing here and [[fishing]] is possible, the game considers this location to be underground.  Therefore, [[Foraging|forageable]] items and [[Artifact Spot|artifact spots]] never spawn here.\n\n==Quests==\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width:80%; min-width:500px;\"\n! style=\"width:8%\" | Quest Name\n! style=\"width:23%\" | Quest Text\n! style=\"width:14%\" | Provided By\n! style=\"width:23%\" | Requirements\n! style=\"width:12%\" | Rewards\n|-\n|[[Quests#Dark Talisman|Dark Talisman]]\n|''The Wizard asked me to retrieve the magic ink from his ex-wife's house... but to gain access I'll need a dark talisman. Enter the sewer and ask [[Krobus]] about the dark talisman.''\n|Enter the [[Railroad]] area after completing the [[Community Center]] [[Bundles]] or the [[Joja Community Development Form]].\n|Speak to [[Krobus]] to gain entrance to the Mutant Bug Lair, then retrieve the Dark Talisman. Return to the [[Railroad]] area and place the Dark Talisman on the artifact blocking the cave. \n|\n*Unlocks the quest [[Quests#Goblin Problem|Goblin Problem]]\n|}\n\n==Fishing==\n[[File:MutantBugLairDistances.png|thumb|right|300px|[[Fishing#Distance from Land|Distances from land]] in the Mutant Bug Lair]]\nThe [[Slimejack]] is a unique [[fish]] that can only be caught in the Mutant Bug Lair. [[Carp]], [[Green Algae]], and [[White Algae]] are also possible. The available fish are the same year-round. Fishing here is dangerous because [[Mutant Fly|Mutant Flies]] continuously spawn and attack the player. To avoid this, fish right at the entrance before any bugs are triggered.\n\n{{FishLocations Mutant Bug Lair}}\n\n==Gallery==\n<gallery mode=packed widths=100% heights=100%>\nMutant Bug Lair Passage.png|The passage inside [[The Sewers]] which [[Krobus]] opens.\nTalisman Chest.png|The talisman chest.\n</gallery>\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.1|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.11|[[Weeds]] in the Mutant Bug Lair no longer change with the season or turn into [[Battery Pack]]s during [[Winter]]. Fixed bug where monsters in the Mutant Bug Lair could become the standard grub/fly after saving/reloading the game.}}\n{{History|1.4|Problematic water tiles fixed, making [[Fishing#Distance from Land|distance-from-land calculations]] more consistent.}}\n\n{{NavboxLocations}}\n\n[[Category:Locations]]\n\n[[de:Mutantenkäferhöhle]]\n[[es:Madriguera de bichos mutantes]]\n[[fr:Repaire des insectes mutants]]\n[[it:Covo di insetti mutanti]]\n[[ja:ミュータントバグのすみか]]\n[[ko:돌연변이 곤충 둥지]]\n[[hu:Mutáns Rovar Odú]]\n[[pt:Covil dos Insetos Mutantes]]\n[[ru:Логово жуков-мутантов]]\n[[tr:Mutant Böcek Yuvası]]\n[[zh:突变虫穴]]"
